      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## HABA Production Monitor\nTabele gata facute pentru `Laser1`, `Abkant`, operatori si programe.\n\nRecomandare: foloseste panourile de randament real, nu media simpla pe foi. Valorile sunt calculate ca `total cutting sau bending / total machine on * 100`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count by (operator_name) (max_over_time(haba_saved_cycle_completed{machine_key=\"laser1\"}[3650d]))",
          "format": "time_series",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{operator_name}}",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Laser1 / Operatori / Total Foi",
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (operator_name) (max_over_time(haba_saved_cycle_cutting_seconds{machine_key=\"laser1\"}[3650d])) / sum by (operator_name) (max_over_time(haba_saved_cycle_machine_on_seconds{machine_key=\"laser1\"}[3650d])) * 100",
          "format": "time_series",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{operator_name}}",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Laser1 / Operatori / Randament Real",
      "type": "table"
